discussion.content:
The correct response among those offered must be (C) Rip and replace:
1. The app MUST be cloud-resident;
2. A feasibility study has been COMPLETED;
3. The app can only run on the current non-cloud infrastructure.
(A) Lift and shift requires a cloud-ready app – contradicts #3;
(B) Hybrid implies that parts may be migrated, and others remain – contradicts #1 & #3;
(D) In-place upgrade utilizes the existing non-cloud infrastructure – contradicts #1 (plus fails to reduce capital expenses).
